import React from 'react'

function NewInventoryForm() {
  return (
    <form className='new-inventory-form'>
      <label>
        Details

      </label>
      <label>
        
        <select className='category'>
        Category

      </label>
      <input type="submit" value="Add Inventory"/>

    </form>
   )
}

export default NewInventoryForm
